  "detailed_description": "This is by a person to develop a fighting  without fighting mechanism game.<br><br><br>No gorgeous scenes, no sexy characters.<br>Skills do not need to rub, only press down.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433460/extras/1b9f22b4eb2eeedb2ebec1b387655bef.avif?t=1695912938\" width=344 height=136 /></span><br><br><br>The damage reduction mechanism and the overlord armor mechanism make the battle more challenging.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433460/extras/01888c40ac3c7a48adcca5a1df3528cf.avif?t=1695912938\" width=306 height=456 /></span><br><br><br>All kinds of throwing skills, judge skills, invincible skills, displacement skills, make the battle more maneuverable.<br>Every character has a big skill, But it starts with a skill cooldown.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433460/extras/777c32803c8ae11000eac5f96562bdee.avif?t=1695912938\" width=388 height=428 /></span><br><br>You can play 1v1 against your friends.<br>Or one person playing PVE.<br>Of course, you can also enter practice mode to familiarize yourself with the operation or tricks!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433460/extras/307aecc8a19b320171c297b3a0ca7961.avif?t=1695912938\" width=760 height=426 /></span><br><br><br>If you're confused about a skill, check out the in-game skill description.<br>It's just a simple description, but it may help you.<br>There are five roles in the current version.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433460/extras/10572ede67c605d3d0135ffbf144a77a.avif?t=1695912938\" width=760 height=426 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "This is by a person to develop a fighting  without fighting mechanism game.<br><br><br>No gorgeous scenes, no sexy characters.<br>Skills do not need to rub, only press down.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433460/extras/1b9f22b4eb2eeedb2ebec1b387655bef.avif?t=1695912938\" width=344 height=136 /></span><br><br><br>The damage reduction mechanism and the overlord armor mechanism make the battle more challenging.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433460/extras/01888c40ac3c7a48adcca5a1df3528cf.avif?t=1695912938\" width=306 height=456 /></span><br><br><br>All kinds of throwing skills, judge skills, invincible skills, displacement skills, make the battle more maneuverable.<br>Every character has a big skill, But it starts with a skill cooldown.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433460/extras/777c32803c8ae11000eac5f96562bdee.avif?t=1695912938\" width=388 height=428 /></span><br><br>You can play 1v1 against your friends.<br>Or one person playing PVE.<br>Of course, you can also enter practice mode to familiarize yourself with the operation or tricks!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433460/extras/307aecc8a19b320171c297b3a0ca7961.avif?t=1695912938\" width=760 height=426 /></span><br><br><br>If you're confused about a skill, check out the in-game skill description.<br>It's just a simple description, but it may help you.<br>There are five roles in the current version.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433460/extras/10572ede67c605d3d0135ffbf144a77a.avif?t=1695912938\" width=760 height=426 /></span>",
